---
title: Teach computing. With confidence.
layout: layout
fixed: true
---

<section class='header-block'>
  <a href="http://vimeo.com/141552266" class="video-link">
    <div class="border-wrapper" title="Play Video">
      <%= inline_svg "assets/school/triangle.svg", class: "icon white" %>
    </div>
  </a>

  <h1 class="animated fadeIn">
    Last month, our members spent 24,700 hours using Codio.
  </h1>

  <div class="action-buttons animated fadeInUp">
    <%= link_to 'Start FREE Trial', '/p/free-education-trial', class: 'button button-large button-main' %>
    <%= link_to 'Book a Demo', 'https://attendee.gotowebinar.com/rt/2969360162613017601', class: 'button button-large' %>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="school-content">
  <div id="school-content-start"></div>

  <div
    class="school-section school-section-content wow fadeIn"
    data-wow-duration="2s"
    data-wow-delay=".5s"
    >
    <h2>Unique learning experience</h2>

    <%= image_tag 'assets/school/laptop-ide.png', class: "school-section-content-img" %>
    <div class="school-section-content-copy">
      <p>
        Codio course content is made interactive with live code and preview windows
        &mdash; allowing students to test and trial what they're learning; built in
        challenges also stimulate engagement and create opportunities for "learning by doing".
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <div class="school-section school-section-curriculum">
    <div
      class="school-section-left wow fadeIn"
      data-wow-duration="1s"
      data-wow-delay="0s"
      >
      <h2>Full curriculum coverage</h2>
      <p>
        From Computer systems, computational and algorithmic thinking challenges,
        courses on Python and Javascript, as well as all the project workspace you
        need &mdash; Codio empowers you to teach the full Computing curriculum with
        confidence.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="school-section-right school-section-curriculum-img wow fadeInRight"
      data-wow-duration="1s"
      data-wow-delay=".8s"
      ></div>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <div
    class="school-section school-section-assessments wow fadeIn"
    data-wow-duration="2s"
    data-wow-delay=".5s"
    >
    <div class="school-section-left">
      <h2>Integrated assessments</h2>
      <p>
        Teacher dashboards display clear and simple information about Class and
        Student progress &mdash; presenting scores for built-in auto-marked
        assessments that enable you to focus more time on teaching and supporting
        and less on administration.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="school-section-right school-section-assessments-img"></div>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <div class="school-section school-section-projects">
    <div
      class="school-section-projects-top wow fadeIn"
      data-wow-duration="2s"
      data-wow-delay=".5s"
      >
      <h2>Perfect for projects</h2>
      <p>
        Accessible anywhere, with pre-configured environments containing all
        the software and other components a student will need, each user enjoys
        a dedicated virtual server for their project work &mdash; ideal in the
        classroom or at home.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="school-section-projects-bottom">
      <div
        class="school-section-projects-img wow fadeInUp"
        data-wow-duration="1s"
        data-wow-delay=".5s"
        >
        <%= image_tag 'assets/school/live-code.png' %>
        <figcaption>Live code</figcaption>
      </div>
      <div
        class="school-section-projects-img wow fadeInUp"
        data-wow-duration="1s"
        data-wow-delay="1s"
        >
        <%= image_tag 'assets/school/preview-windows.png' %>
        <figcaption>Preview windows</figcaption>
      </div>
      <div
        class="school-section-projects-img wow fadeInUp"
        data-wow-duration="1s"
        data-wow-delay="1.5s"
        >
        <%= image_tag 'assets/school/challenges.png' %>
        <figcaption>Challenges</figcaption>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <div class="school-section school-section-partners">
    <h2>
      We are proud members and partners of
    </h2>
    <div class="school-section-partners-img">
      <%= image_tag 'assets/school/partners-ocr.png' %>
      <%= image_tag 'assets/school/partners-cas.png' %>
      <%= image_tag 'assets/school/partners-naace.png' %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <%= partial "call-to-action" %>
</section>
